snippet.title: Ping Pong Flix
snippet.description:
Welcome back to the Ping Pong Flix for all up to date Entertainment topics in popular genre films. My name is Chris Wong-Swenson and I LOVE to discuss, report, and speculate on all popular genre films and shows in the entertainment industry! My bread and butter however are DC movie news and DCEU upcoming movies and a little Marvel.  I'm also one of the many Associate Producers for Zack Snyder's Justice League!
